text: Frederick Harold Naylor (15 February 1881 - 16 November 1949) was a British swimmer, from Jersey. He competed in the men's 200 metre breaststroke event at the 1908 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1881 births Category:1949 deaths Category:British male swimmers Category:Olympic swimmers of Great Britain Category:Swimmers at the 1908 Summer Olympics Category:Jersey male swimmers
